title: Marketplace Roundtable #14: The Insiders' Edge With Bret Jensen
description: Bret Jensen (aka The Insiders Forum) sits down with SA's Jonathan Liss to discuss his unique approach to investing. Particularly when company insiders are buying up their own shares en masse, Jensen starts to dig deeper, developing a thesis for the stock. It's a strategy that has routinely delivered out-sized returns over the years, as demonstrated by the strong performance of his SA Marketplace service, The Insiders Forum.
